releaseNotes:
1.0.59 - add interface Apply, DeleteFlag, Callback
1.0.58 - Remove Null data saat passing ke JSend agar tampilan error msg bersih.
1.0.57 - Trow() di Boolean Extension passingkan error message ke listError, tidak hanya ke msgError saja. Supaya terdeteksi oleh JSend()
1.0.56 - Add Alter() With CallBack function di Abstract Builder
1.0.55 - Ubah Interface BuilderStrap() menjadi Abstract Class karena implementasinya sama untuk semua class turunan
1.0.54 - Advanced Builder Pattern Helper; Add Alter(), AlterIf(), Mutate(), HaltOn()
1.0.53 - Add JSend Compliant untuk api result
1.0.52 - Change Builder.FromModel() to be more generic, and add BuilderStrap()
1.0.51 - add ChangeState() di builder
1.0.50 - Remove Null Property saat build pattern
1.0.49 - Adding ModelStateDictionary generator from ValidationError (FV)
1.0.48 - Adding Transformer to Builder
1.0.47 - Fixing Bug
1.0.46 - Command di interface Builder Pattern dibuat sanggup command tanpa parameter
1.0.45 - Command di interface Builder Pattern dibuat sanggup terima parameter sampe 4 buah
1.0.44 - Refactor Builder Pattern
1.0.43 - Builder FromCommand tambah interface ICommand<T> (satu parameter)
1.0.42 - Add RemoveNull() and AbstractClass BuilderT
1.0.41 - Add Builder Pattern Helper
1.0.40 - Fixing-Bug; AppendLine di Serialisasi ValidateException dipindah ke akhir.
1.0.39 - Add extension utk serialisasi error msg dari ValidationException.
1.0.38 - Add CommandException, derived form ValidationException (FluentValidation)
1.0.37 - Fixing namespace for pattern-helper
1.0.36 - Add support for Command Pattern (ICommand and AbstractManipulator)
1.0.35 - Add CustomValidator format jam HH:mm (contoh: 09:23)
1.0.34 - Extension .Throw() ubah menjadi ValidationException (sebelumnya ArgumentException)
1.0.32 - Add Throw Extension (ValidationException)
1.0.31 - Add extension Max(), Min(), Between for int; IfNot() for boolean
1.0.30 - Add extension Join for Collection (IEnumerable)
1.0.29 - Add IfNotNull() extension
1.0.28 - Add extension untuk cek duplikasi data string
1.0.27 - Polymorph Similarty; With FuzzyLimit and Check JWScore
1.0.26 - Add string extension: InvalidEmail, SimplePassword, Hash256
1.0.25 - Change Parameter Location in Throw Boolean extender for consistency
1.0.24 - Boolean extender Throw() now deliver error data as well
1.0.23 - Re-compile
1.0.22 - Add DateTime Extension: IsValidTgl(), IsValidJam()
1.0.21 - Add DateTime Extension: ToTglDMY(), ToTglYMD(), ToDate(), GetHariName()
1.0.20 - Bug Fix String.Truncate; function nor respect lengt in argument
1.0.19 - Extension String.Include(); Searching multiple word ignore case and ignore order
1.0.18 - Add string extension ToTglYMD() and ToTglDMY()
1.0.17 - Add SqlCommand Helper
1.0.16 - Add String Extension In(), NotIn() and AnyNullProp()
